  m_Name: Resident 2B
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueData
  SpeakerName: 
  lines:
  - I hate that I have to look at my ugly ceiling in the bathroom every time I go
    in there.
  - "There\u2019s a piece hanging from the wall and it looks horrible with those
    cracks and holes."
  - "It\u2019s been about a week since that leak was fixed there. Is it possible
    to have it fixed today"
